<para>Calls <ref refid="namespaceSTM32Board_1a3785a13cc5ed58de231b71fd5e143f00" kindref="member">STM32Board::begin()</ref>, starts the UART at 250000 baud, configures a pass-all CAN filter, then calls canStart(). Call STM32Board::setDebug(true) before this to enable diagnostic output.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>uartPort</parametername>
