<parameterdescription>
<para>Hardware serial port connected to the RP2040 <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref>. Use Serial2 (UART2 PA2/PA3) on the standard master board. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
